name "cha:conclusion"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This thesis explored the use of tangible objects as hosts for digital content,
 added via spatial augmented reality, in a variety of contexts.
 More specifically, we have focused on the interaction with the digital
 content as well as using these augmented objects as a basis to foster introspec
tion.
 Each chapter presented thus far have presented and discussed their individual
 contributions.
 In this chapter, we summarize these contributions and discuss potential
 future works, with a more global approach.
\end_layout

