key "Weiser1996"

\end_inset

, we think that this combination of fields could present great opportunities
 for fostering calm and wellbeing.
 Even more so, with technology designed for self-reflection, people could
 investigate how their own inner states are affected by different stimuli
 and events.
\end_layout

